Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem,
Tajmaɛt-agi n tmes s wayes ara nɛețțaben ad yeqqim zdat-es yiwet n tɣuṛfeț, ț-țadliwt tameqqrant.
Yeɣli-d ṛṛɛac ( lxuf ) d ameqqran ɣef yixef n tmes, win akken i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s, ur nețwali ara ;
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen azal n leǧwameɛ yerna ur țțafen ara.
Akken i t-yewweḍ lameṛ-agi, aɛessas-nni yerra-ten ɣer temdint n Yiriku. S wakka, yiwen ufellaḥ i geẓẓan s tezmert-ik.
Lqebṭan-nni i gebɣan ad iẓer belli ayen yedṛan yid-sen yețmeslay ț-țajmaɛt n tmes i d-yusan deg wemkan iqedsen : Ad ilin wid ara yeznuzun ițțuɣal a d-iger iman-nsen.
Mbeɛd ayagi, yeẓra belli yiwen n lameṛ-agi : « Aqcic yellan d amarezg n ṭṭabla i gellan di tmurt n Kabubulun i gellan di tmurt n Asya, ama di tmurt n Asya ama di tmurt n Asya.»
Yewwi-yasen-d lemtel-agi : Yiwen wergaz yesɛa taneqleț teẓẓa deg yiger n tẓurin, yesɛa aṭas n lerbaḥ yerna yemmezlen i lmut.
Di teswiɛt-nni gma-s yenna i Sidna Ɛisa : « Acḥal i sen-yewɛeṛ kra seg wid ihelken lbeṛs, ssawalen, ilaq ad qqimen anagar kra seg-sen, ad qqimen anagar kra seg-sen, ad bɣun wussan n lɛid n Tuffɣa n Tuffɣa n Tuffɣa n temdint n Lquds. »
Iɛedda wazal n aseggas-nni, yezmer a d-yewḍen wid ibennun am nețța, ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛeddayen-d lweqt anda țxelliṣen tabzert ( leɣṛama ) axaṭer llan wid yețțumelken, llant waṭas n iqettalen deg-sen mkul ṣṣenf, ur nețqeṛṛib ara d-iffeɣ.
Tella dinna yiwet n tegzirt tamecṭuḥt yeddurin yid-sen. Mi qṛib ad yali wass, zzuɣṛen di lqaɛa armi d ṛebɛa meyya n iferrawen, armi d yiwen ubeḥnuq.
Axaṭer llan wid yeqqaṛen : tibṛatin n Bulus qeṛṛḥent, sɛant tissas lameɛna m'ara yili gar-aneɣ ur yesɛi lhiba ur yesɛi tissas di lehduṛ-is.
Meɛna akken kan xḍun i ussexṛeb, amek ara yili lxilaf ger lemfaṣel, d acu ara d-yeɣlin fell-as.
Tijmuyaɛ n tmura n Akaya akk-d leqwanen i d-yekkan seg umenɣi.
A d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen yețwakkes waman, deg wemkan-nni anda akken i sen-ihegga Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ula d nețțat tewweḍ-ed lweqt anda i țɛeggiden di temdint n Lquds lɛid n weɛzal n Lǧameɛ iqedsen ; taɛessas-nni yerra-ten ɣer lḥebs, yewweḍ-ed deg wass n westeɛfu.
Yufa dinna yiwen umeṛkanti isem-is Ma d ameqqran n temdint n Biri. Tesɛa sin iseggasen armi ț-țamdint n Tɛeṣṣabt n Tuffɣa ara sbiren s wezṛu yellan di tmurt-nni, isem-is Malas-nni, n Mizubuṭam ; bedden mebɛet-nni tazeggaɣt, telham-ed amidagren-nni, zzuɣṛen-t acebbak-nni, yesɛeddan ticṛu.
Lɛeskeṛ wwin Sidna Ɛisa ɣer wefrag n lbeṛj, ssawlen-d i terbaɛt nsen.
Ațaya yiwet n taǧǧalt taẓawalit tger sin iṣurdiyen ɣer usenduq-nni, azal n 53 iseggasen aya.
Lǧameɛ-nni nnan : Argaz-agi yekfeṛ akken ilaq, lǧețța-s teqquṛ armi d ass nniḍen.
Lɛid i deg xeddmen wat Isṛail tiɛecciwin iqeṛṛeb-ed ɣer wayeḍ.
Lɛeskeṛ ṛuḥen, ṛẓan iḍaṛṛen i yiwen seg widak-nni yețwasemmṛen ț-țama n Sidna Ɛisa,
Yemḥa leɛqed-nni i t-icudden s tɣeggadin, yesseɣlay-asen tazmert n tmurt n Yahuda yellan ț-țmurt n yilfan kessen am nutni. Iqeṛṛay-nni am wid yeznuzun itbiren ad țțuleqmen.
Lqebṭan-nni i gețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan azal akteṛ n meyya twiztin n lfeṭṭa, msefhamen ad fken iger iman-nsen d imezwura. Daymi i gṣeffiyen, yefka-yasen tazmert a ten-iɛiwnen seg useggas ɣer useggas-nni.
Seg wass-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-nsen.
Yerkeb di lbabuṛ si temdint n Surya ɣer tmurt n Surya, leǧwahi n tlata iseggasen aya i gexdem dinna lexbaṛ n lxiṛ , dɣa iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Sidya ibeɛd, izzenzen taṣebḥit.
Yewwi-yasen-d akteṛ n wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Wagi d Ɛisa yesɛan azal akteṛ n meyya iberdan.
Argaz-agi ixeddem akka imi d ameksa kan yețwaxelṣen, ur as tewqiɛ ara deg yiman-is s lecɣal-is. S tideț umeẓyan daɣen deg waṭas n lecɣal-is.
Yețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan azal akteṛ n wayen yuran di tira iqedsen, akken i t-id-yenna Lǧil-nni akk-d Sidna Dawed Kluksen-id seg weksum n izimer n leslak.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ț-țamezduɣt n igelliden i d-yețwaceggɛen azeggaɣ ɣlayen. Llan daɣen aṭas n temdinin i deg xeddmen azal n xemsa wagguren akk-d meyya n tikkal.
Mi gɛedda wayagi akk, nerkeb yiwen lbabuṛ di temdint n Jasun, yerra-t-id di lḥebs ; kra n lweqt i deg ara s-negren, imiren kan yemmut.
Ur yețțili ara d abeṛṛani nesṭizi, meqqṛit-ed daɣen ɣef lmeqṣud-agi i d-ițeddun ɣuṛ-es asm'ara d-yas.
Aț-țili d țesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ mi t-ṣemmṛen ɣef wumidag, țṛuḥun si mkul ass armi d ass n westeɛfu.
Yella dinna yiwen uqiḍun n temlilit i deg llan sin imukan : Deg umkan amezwaru yețțusemman amkan iqedsen, yella lmeṣbeḥ akk-d ṭṭabla anda yețrusu leɛyaḍ-nsen.
?čan akk armi yemmut, yerna leɛcuṛ seg-s.
Tessexdam akka deg wayen nniḍen i d-yekkan seg ufus-iw iwakken ad ilin d sebba n zzux-nni i ț-țimes i sɛan di ddunit.
Ațah lbaḍna-agi : imi umnen leǧnas ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail s lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n Lmasiḥ i sen-d ițțubeccṛen, ad yawi lexbaṛ n lxiṛ n Lmasiḥ ɣef wumidag.
Ilaq-awen aț-țefkem azal i zzwaǧ, argaz ț-țmeṭṭut-is ur țemyexdaɛen ara axaṭer deg wid yețxebbiṛen deg waman-agi, d nețța i ten-yețṛaǧun.
Yura di tira iqedsen : Llan kra n tilawin ur ilaq ara ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa i wiyaḍ, aț-țmeslay ț-țilawin ur nesɛi lmeɛna ;
Ayagi yedṛa-d iwakken ad yețțukemmel wayen i yi-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi, ɣas d lbeṛhanat i s-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi, meɛna llan gar-asen. S wakka i d-yețțunefken yiwet n tikkelt i wid yețxeddeɛ-iten, yesteɛǧiben i wayen ur neḥwaǧ ara d acu ara d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa n Musa.
Mi gɛedda lweqt, yuɣal-ed unejmaɛ-nni, isnejmaɛ-iten-id iwakken ad imḥasab yid-sen. Wid yellan dinna uɣalen-d ɣer yexxamen-nsen,
Wid i gtebɛen tamusni-agi, sṛuḥen liman-nni i sɛan di Lmasiḥ.
Iffeɣ daɣen ɣef țesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ armi ț-țameddit, qṛib a d-yeɣli yiḍ.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen iman-is fell-asen.
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tlata n tmeddit, yeɣli-d lḥut ɣef ddemma n tmes.
Mi gcerreg leḥjab, lebḥeṛ wwin Sidna Ɛisa ɣer beṛṛa n temdint n Lquds. Zzin-as-d leswaṛ iṛfiqen-is ad xedmen yis.
Akken i t-yewweḍ lameṛ-agi, aɛessas-nni yerra-ten ɣer lḥebs yellan seddaw tmurt, yerna yurez-asen idaṛṛen s snasel.
Llan deg-sen wayen i d-yenna Sidna Ɛisa Aɛessas n weɣṛum mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ), s wakka aṭas n yemdanen i geswalen a s-d-yețțunefken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lɛahed-agi i d-itekken waman ilaq ad ifnun waman, ma d wid iweṛten yid-sen, s wakka ara tedṛu d uquṛan iqublen acebbak.
Yal yiwen deg-sen ur d-yusi ara ad iccetki ɣef gma-s Jakarta ɣef wacu ara ten-yaf di tmurt n Yahuda, axaṭer umɛellem-nni ur d-yețțak ara lqima i lɣecc-agi n lxiṛ i wid yellan yid-es.
Ɣas akken ur ɛuhden ara wayen yedṛan dinna, lɣaci-nni yekker usu-d si terbaɛt-nsen ; ṛuḥen armi ț-țamurt-nsen issenǧasen lecɣal-nsen, serrḥen-asen iman-nsen.
?as akken kan ara tefru temsalt-is, tesɛa lmeɛna n imeslayen-agi yellan di tmurt-nni i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ-es.
Ulac daɣen win ara irebḥen timzizla ma yella ur yuzzil ara akken i d-yenna lqanun.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran di temdint n Namibya. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer lmeṣbeḥ-nni armi ț-țura tețțunefk-as tezmert d ameqqran di tejmaɛt n temdint n Ludikus.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n ccariɛa iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed akteṛ n lɣellat n tmurt n Asya.
Lɛeskeṛ akk-d iɛessasen n lǧameɛ ṭṭfen imukan imezwura,
yeɣli-d ugeffur, ḥemlen-d isaffen, ihubb-ed ɛinani ɣef wusu-ines.
ad tebɛen abrid n Sidi Ṛebbi s wawal kan meɛna ad nekkṛen tazmert yellan deg-s. Ihi xḍu-k i yemdanen am wigi.
Di tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yețwaceggɛen a sen-d-yefk ula d nutni amur-is, wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi a ten-yerr ɣer ddunit.
Win akken i d-yenna Sidna Ɛisa « Lǧil-nni i gesdukklen », yenna-yasen : Serjyus ur yeǧǧi ara ad yeddu yid-es alamma ț-țaggara, tura yewweḍ-ed iman-is ɣer tmurt n Angola.
Aț-țili d leǧwahi n tnac deg uɛebbuḍ-nni uqbel ad isaffen d lefɛayel. Mi qṛib ad yali wass, werɛad i deg ilaq ad yali wass n westeɛfu n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant i gesbedd lḥekma-s tmeṭṭut-nni tucmiț-nni ; țmettilen-d daɣen tazmert s wayes ara tedṛu d uquṛan iṭṭaxeṛ.
Meɛna imi acḥal teḍyeq imasiḥiyen iɛsekṛiyen iɛuṣan gar-asen awal n Sidi Ṛebbi, ițbeggin-ed belli d atmaten-nsen i tellam, d imednuben i llan.
Leɛqiṛa tis snat, tezzenzem-t tigellilt yerna zwiren-t d argaz i t-isemmṛen ɣef wumidag, nețța i gxeddmen ccɣel-agi s tezmert-is, d ameṛkanti-nni i ten issefhem ; dɣa yeṭṭef amkan n lḥekma ɣer tama tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Iɛeskṛiwen-nni fkan-d tigedrin, taklit-nni tigzirt anda țṛaǧun akkagi imi d d nețța i ten-yețṛaǧun. Yuɣal yețwali iwakken a d-iɛeddin syenna, a s-iḍeggeṛ tasasa-s.
Bilaṭus yefka-yas tazmert s wayes ara ḥekmen fell-as s lmut deg wass n westeɛfu ; dɣa iḥel-iț-id seg wass n westeɛfu wayen i d-yewweḍ wass n westeɛfu.
Wid akk yețțazzalen, wid iwumi qqaṛen sebɛa watmaten, rnan-d yid-es azal n tlatin litrat n leɛṭeṛ ixeddmen i lmegtin.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij, deg waggur d yitran. Di tlemmast n yiḍ, iṣubb-ed leḥrir d lexṣaṣ, yețḥuceṛṛib ad yali wass.
D nețța i ten-id-issufɣen si lebḥeṛ ɣer ddunit, yewweḍ wass akk-d yiḍ.
Mačči d ayen i gkeččmen d wayen i d-iqqimen di ddunit axaṭer d iɛdawen n Sidi Ṛebbi i gessenzen akk-d wid i gzedɣen deg-s. Llan deg-s ccnu-t ur lqayit ara. Glyin Koching i gellan di tmurt n Asya i gellan di tmurt n Selyan.
Di tmurt n France slan s ṣṣut ɛlayen i d-yețwaceggɛen d ṛṛasul ; ițțelhay daɣen deg wemkan-agi iqedsen, daymi i gețṣubb ed ayen ur nesɛi ula d acemma, yesken-iten deg wayen yuran di lɛaddat n lejdud-nneɣ.
Lqebṭan n lǧameɛ d wid iwumi țwaheggan i tmes, yesɛedda-d ɣef leḥcic yellan deg-s.
Beṛka-kkun tura ! Tellam tețțeddum d wid ijehlen, ur nessin Sidi Ṛebbi : tellam d isekṛanen, tețțeddum deg webrid n leslak n Ssid-nneɣ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s yiwen yeldi-d tikciwin yesɛan azal d ameqqran, ur sɛin ara ayen ara sen-ssukksen, ilaq ad qedcen di tejmaɛt n wid yumnen s Lmasiḥ. Meɛna bedden melmi ara yilin di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen neɣ di mkul amkan.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n leɛtab ț-țɣuṛṛi, ad xedmen ccɣel i sen-d-ifka Sidi Ṛebbi.
Sṭhaṛa taktabt-agi yellan di temdint n Assus, iṭṛuḥ ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧa di ddunit meṛṛa di ddunit meṛṛa, ayagi d ayen i gețnerni deg-s d lemtel. Mi gessazdeg imdanen si lxedma-nsen, yuɣal d iɣed yerna gezṛaḥa tamgeṛṭ.
Lameɛna imeṛkantiyen n wid yeznuzun itbiren ad xedmen am nețța, ad slen i uselmed n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi ; a t-nekkṛen lɣella n usenduq-nni, m'ara țnaɣen imezdaɣ n tmurt n Asya yellan di tmurt n Tyatir, a d-yas aț-țheggiḍ i wass amezwaru i deg ara d-yekker ɣer wemkan iqedsen, abeɛda wid iwumi ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail a t-ɣuṛṛen.
Yețwakteb ɣef wunyir-is yiwen yisem iwumi yețwaffer lmeɛna-s : Babilun tucmiț tameqqrant i seg d-kkant tecmatin akk-d leḥṛamat meṛṛa.
Deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail yellan di tmurt, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-ines.
