Tella dinna snat n temzirt, drus i deg ur nesɛi ara tazmert ; temḥeqṛem i leḥḥun deg webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger n win i grebḥen ccix-agi, ur nfennu ara kan i gețṭaren ikuffuṛen iman-nsen.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Tețɣuṛṛu abrid yețțawin ɣer lqaɛa, ur yenfiɛ ara aṭas n yedrimen i d-itekken si temdint n Lquds. Lameɛna ulli-agi yezmer ad iheggi abrid ajdid iwakken a d-afen tamɛict-nwen.
Tajmaɛt-nni n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, igellil ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wayen ara ḥwiǧen, iwakken ad inin iwekklen wid ihelken. Deg-s yemmuten, ad yefk tazmert s wayes ara tenɣalen.
Tețțubarek win i d-yusan s ɣuṛ Ṛebbi mi d-yusa ccariɛa n Ṛuman. Tuɣalfi-agi tbanent-ed seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed wasif. Iferrawen-nni, m'ara d-yaweḍ lḥal ad ḥekmen fell-asen s tezmert n Sidi Ṛebbi. Akka ara tedṛu d uselmed-agi i gxeddem.
Tella dinna yiwen umeṛkanti isem-is Akilas, laṣel-is n tmurt n Tqenṭert ; yewweḍ-ed deg ussan-nni kan di temdint n Ifasus i deg ilaq ad ițțuɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s wass-nni, armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Asmi gemmut Stifan, yekker uqehheṛ i gessemfaṛaqen inelmaden ɣer mkul amkan ; ṛuḥen armi ț-țamurt n umenɣi ɣef ddemma-nsen nutni yellan ț-țzemmar n wuzzal ț-țizegzawin i deg heggin iman-nsen.
