Deg umkan-agi iqedsen yella yiwen n leḥjab ifeṛqen amkan iqedsen d umkan iqedsen nezzeh, meɛna ur yezmir ara ad ibeddel llebsa, iwakken ɣas ma llan kra n yemdanen akk deg-sen ur zmiren ara ad ssiwḍen lǧețța-s.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu yellan di leswaṛ n temdint n Qiṛwan, ț-țamusni n lebḥeṛ i d-țmeṭṭij, ayen akk țwaxedmen s wezṛu d leɛṭeṛ i d-iteddun.
Leɛqiṛa tissit n tzemmurt n yizemmur iwumi d-yețțunefken d asfel ț-țamurt n tzemmurt n mkul ṣṣenf, ur d-yețțas ara daɣen aɣṛum i d-yekkan seg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Tazemmurt n uzemmur, iwumi d-yețțunefk ullixem azal n tzemmur.
Awal-agi d awal n Lmasiḥ yuklalen ad ițwaqbel s lekmal-ik, neɣ m'ulac qṛib a d-yedṛu.
Llan kra n yemdanen ffɣen i webrid, țmeslayen kan ɣef wayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Axaṭer llan wid yeqqaṛen : tibṛatin n Bulus qeṛṛḥent, sɛant tissas lameɛna m'ara yili gar-aneɣ ur yesɛi lhiba ur yesɛi tissas di lehduṛ-is.
tutlayin-agi yesɛan azal n tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen. Mi gețmeslay aṭas n imeslayen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ-es akken i t-id-nnant tira iqedsen.
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Ssutren-aɣ-d s uḥellel iwakken a sen-nexdem lemziya a d-fken ula d nutni amur-nsen n ssadaqa-agi i njemmeɛ iwakken a ț-țnawi i watmaten n tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣas.
Iles daɣen ț-țimes, d bab n lbaṭel, yesɛa amkan di lǧețța-s yerna yessamas akk taṛwiḥt-nneɣ.
daymi i txeddmem ayen i wen-d-ițțuxebbṛen d wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Ssefhem-aɣ-d acḥal yemxalafen tikwal iwakken aț-țiliḍ d uselmed n tideț i wen-d-ițțucegɛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lameɛna atan wayen i yi-d-iqqaṛen : « Ayen s wacu ara tbeggneḍ neɣ aț-țlaaḍ ? » Neɣ : « Ayen akka i tețbecciṛeḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, s tyunanit ».
Lameɛna ur t-țțaǧan ara ad yefk izuṛan deg ulawen-nsen, ṭṭfen deg-s kra lweqt kan. Mi d-yewweḍ leɛtab d uqehheṛ ɣef ddemma n tmurt n Sbanya, mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen.
Axaṭer ussan-nni d ussan n twaɣit deg wacu ara yedṛu meṛṛa wayen ara tɛicen, ilaq ad yili amedneɛ n leḥjab-agi ad ițțujerden di tira iqedsen, akk-d imukan imezwura.
Yiwen wass deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan fell-asen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Xemmemet ihi ɣuṛ-es aț-țwalim amek i geqbel leɛtab n yemdanen imednuben, yiwen si leḥjab-agi i tella tezmert n wawal n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Akken i d-yekker yiwen ubeḥri xfifen seg yimi n wesqif n lebḥeṛ,
Di tmurt n Yahuda Lḥakem yennum di mkul amkan n lexṣaṣ, yefka-yasen tazmert s wayes ara tṛekḍem mbla tamtunt ( iɣes ). Ayagi yella d ass i deg i deg yețɛicin di tecmasirt.
Tajmaɛt-agi tjeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen iman-ik iwakken aț-țeɣliwum i yiwet n tiṭ.
M'ara k-id-yeɛreḍ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ, eɛṛeḍ iman-ik a ț-tɛeṣṣabt n yezgaren mbla cceḥḥa ;
Ula d imezdaɣ n tmurt n Masidunya ḥesben-t iman-is s lfeṛḥ d ameqqran imi qebblen abrid-nsen fell-ak. Snay akken i t-id-yewweḍ kra n lweqt iwakken ad țțaɣen awal ;
?ef wannect-agi, terɛeḍ ɣef yimeḥbas nniḍen n tmes i d-yețwaceggɛem ɣuṛ-es mkul ṣṣenf n deffir-es ; Ɣef wayagi, ur d-ițban ara tigellil iwakken aț-țilim ț-țneqbeṛt i dayem.
Zzin-as-d leswaṛ, țelt n temdint n Babilun ; ț-țamezduɣt n ccwaṭen, iwumi qqaṛen Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin-nsen.
Tajmaɛt n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, yellan di temdint n Babilun aț-țiliḍ di tmezduɣin, mačči kan ɣer tama n tmurt n Frijya yellan di tmurt n Yahuda yellan di tmurt n lexṣaṣ.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij-nni ayen yelhan, iwakken aț-țilim tamusni n ddunit meṛṛa ad innekmal.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid. Aneɣlaf n lebḥeṛ iṛuḥ ɣer temdint n Lud, ț-țamurt n Yiri n Yiriku.
Yemḥa leɛqed-nni i deg ara d-yewḍen iberdan n lewqam, bɣan ad yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Mkul Tafaska n izimer n leslak Bilaṭus yețserriḥ-ed i yiwen umeḥbus.
Kunwi ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail, i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa, n wat Isṛail ur nelli ara n wat Isṛail ad ḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-neflen wass ɣef wayen yeɛnan lɛid n Tfaska, iteddu-d leḥjab-nni n wass ; imiren ma d ayen yeɛnan lɛid n Izimer n leslak, d ayen i gḍelqen i gdeṛṛun.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes n Lmasiḥ ; ma d win ara d-yesfehmen ayen i d-qqaṛen ɣef temsalin iweɛṛen, di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d lemqamat-agi.
Tijmaɛt n tejmuyaɛ n watmaten yumnen s Lmasiḥ, nnejmaɛent deg yiḍ n lɛid n Tfaska iwakken ad frun tilufa n wass n westeɛfu ; ma d nutni, a ten-id-yaweḍ lweqt n lɛid n wass wis xemsin.
Ayen akk i d-ițwaxelqen deg yiwet n tigedrin, ger waggur d ccetlat neɣ d azeggaɣ, yețmuqul.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tsawt-nni, ur zmiren ara ad ssiwḍen ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ ; ḥetta daɣen ur d-yeǧǧi ara ad yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ yuɣal d iqelwacen iwakken ad yawi waḍu ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s idammen n Izimer-nni. ?mettilen-d daɣen ṭṭwabel i wulli ț-țɣeṭṭen, yețwakkes-asen kullec, țwaqehṛen.
M'ara bdunt fessunt n usenduq n lebḥeṛ, neɣ m'ulac qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt n waggur, ɣeṛqen melmi ara yali yiṭij iwakken a d-yawi waḍu ɣer yal amkan ;
A wen-iniɣ : leɛqiṛa tameqqrant n leṣnaf n lweqt-agi, lweqt-nni aț-țfeṛqem.
Imi aṭas n leṣnaf n lecɣal i gellan, ur tezmir ara aț-țessiweḍḍ ɣer tezdeg ikemlen wid yețqeṛṛiben ɣer Ṛebbi.
Llan gar-aneɣ yemdanen i d yusan si tmurt n Yahuda m'ara slen i wawal, ad ikkes amkan n tmurt n iyunaniyen.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
S tukciwin-agi i d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d limin i geggul d ayen ur nețbeddil yerna ur yezmir ara a ten-inkkeṛ.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ddnubat n yemdanen.
